    "muctieuid",

    "sodologic",
    "soturack",
    "duongdanfile"

    '{{insert_form.formData.tenhoso}}',
    '{{insert_form.formData.ngaybanhanh}}'

    '{{insert_form.formData.muctieuid}}',
    '{{insert_form.formData.sodotuyencap}}',

    '{{insert_form.formData.duongdanfile}}'
